projects.name: Library of Things
projects.description: A library of things is a collection of items that are loaned out like books. The items are typically things that are not commonly used, such as tools, kitchen appliances, camping equipment and party supplies. The library of things is a great way to reduce waste and save money.

projects.name: Github Finder
projects.description: A simple app to search Github users and view their profile. This app uses the Github API to fetch user data.

projects.name: Ticket Tracker
projects.description: React application using redux with Express and MongoDB. App for submitting tickets for devices. Allows users to respond to notes for each ticket.

projects.name: School House Talk
projects.description: Acts as a single source of truth for communication and information about school activities and events between faculty and parents.
